\f0\b \cf5 \strokec5 5 
\f1\b0 Then the five kings of the Amorites\'97the kings of Jerusalem, Hebron, Jarmuth, Lachish and Eglon\'97joined forces. They moved up with all their troops and took up positions against Gibeon and attacked it.\cf2 \strokec2 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Here is the deal.\uc0\u8232 \
