\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The Israelites weren\'92t under attack\'85the Gibeonites were\uc0\u8232 \
\ls4\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Maybe you didn\'92t know this but we\'92re at war for other people\'92s eternal destinies\uc0\u8232 \
